						<div class="postbody">My progress
<br />
<br />I could not get the x check right.i had them both bcc and no mather what i tried i could not get them to work. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_redface.gif" alt=":oops:" title="Embarassed" /> 
<br />
<br />So .. i read a lot more on the web on collisions and i must say this seems the hardest part of programming games.
<br />
<br />But i have to come up with some kind of box and it simple.
<br />ON PAPER THAT IS. I draw a lot of pictures and its simple.
<br />
<br />If my ball is above the padlle's top or below the bottom or left or right its a miss.
